  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8392994/" class="title-link">值得一读的好书：《太平洋战争》（青梅煮酒著）</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8392994"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/158506319/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/158506319/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">风中的蒲公英</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-03-02"
      class="main-meta">2017-03-02 20:14:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8392994_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  青梅煮酒的《太平洋战争》已经出版了两册：《山雨欲来》和《铤而走险》，说实话，都是值得一读的好书。        作者本人是资深军迷，自然懂得军迷读者想看什么，所以该书会让军迷们读起来大呼过瘾。同时作者的文笔相当不错，讲故事的功夫也很是了得，把一场太平洋战争的来龙去...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8392994/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
